005package edu.wpi.first.hal.can;
006
007/**
008 * Exception indicating that the CAN driver layer has not been initialized. This happens when an
009 * entry-point is called before a CAN driver plugin has been installed.
010 */
011public class CANNotInitializedException extends RuntimeException {
012  private static final long serialVersionUID = -5982895147092686594L;
013
014  public CANNotInitializedException() {
015    super();
016  }
017
018  public CANNotInitializedException(String msg) {
019    super(msg);
020  }
021}
